summary: This document is a certificate from the Department of Transportation certifying the authenticity of records related to the aircraft Bell 430, serial number 49078, registration N430D. It includes signatures from Michelle Endsley and Kevin Jackson, confirming their roles and the validity of the records as of August 23, 2021.

persons.name: Michelle Endsley
persons.context: Michelle Endsley certifies the authenticity of the aircraft records and is identified as the legal custodian of these records.

persons.name: Kevin Jackson
persons.context: Kevin Jackson affirms the validity of the certificate signed by Michelle Endsley.

keyFacts: The document certifies the authenticity of records related to the Bell 430 aircraft.
Michelle Endsley is the legal custodian of the aircraft records.
The certificate was signed and dated on August 23, 2021.
Kevin Jackson is the Acting Manager of the Aircraft Registration Branch.
The document is subject to a protective order.
